<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="20Jul1932"><font color="red">20 July 1932</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): If you write to me please type your letter &hellip; I have written to Faber and Faber offering to pay back the &pound;150 advance of royalties on <i>W.i.P.</i> and cancel the contract. The news today from Feldkirch is better but &hellip; writing seems out of the question. </div>
